      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "XARA'S LEON (8) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 2 lengths away in second (29.98) behind Azzurro at this track. Can find winning form. FABULOUS JONES (4) filled a minor placing last start at Ballarat behind Indian Prince (25.87) in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Leading player again. ASTON LOUISE (5) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 525m behind Azzurro (30.60) in a Maiden FIN. Was in the money the start prior. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PETALI (1) makes debut for the Brendan Pursell kennel. Drawn well and should get his chance. Market should provide a lead to his ability.",
